[Tip 1]
text=_Some buildings (for example, vineyard) have a very small working area, so if building is surrounded with trees and roads, production will stop.
sec=5

[Tip 2]
text=_Watch the fishers hut - after fish resource is exhausted in working area, productin will stop.
sec=4

[Tip 3]
text=_Building process will start only after a road is built to the construction site.
sec=4

[Tip 4]
text=_Be sure to send out a geologist to explore site before building a well or mine.
sec=4

[Tip 5]
text=_Your teritory can be expanded by building various war buildings - Sentry, Fortress, Baracks, etc.
sec=5

[Tip 6]
text=_Miners will work only if supplied with food.
sec=3
